# Clerk Billing (B2C)

This app uses [Clerk Billing](https://clerk.com/docs/nextjs/guides/billing/for-b2c) for subscriptions and payments. Plans and pricing are managed in the Clerk Dashboard — not in Stripe directly.

> Billing is currently in Beta. Pin SDK and `clerk-js` versions to avoid breaking changes.

## Plans

| Slug        | Description       |
|-------------|-------------------|
| `free_user` | Free tier         |
| `pro`       | Paid pro tier     |

## Features

| Slug                      | Description                        |
|---------------------------|------------------------------------|
| `3_decks_limit`           | Limited to 3 decks                 |
| `unlimited_decks`         | Unlimited deck creation            |
| `ai_flashcard_generation` | AI-powered flashcard generation    |

## Pricing Page

Use the `<PricingTable />` component on a dedicated page:

```tsx
// app/pricing/page.tsx
import { PricingTable } from "@clerk/nextjs";

export default function PricingPage() {
  return (
    <div style={{ maxWidth: "800px", margin: "0 auto", padding: "0 1rem" }}>
      <PricingTable />
    </div>
  );
}
```

## Access Control

### Server-side — `has()`

Use `has()` from the `auth()` object to gate access by **plan** or **feature**.

```tsx
import { auth } from "@clerk/nextjs/server";

export default async function ProPage() {
  const { has } = await auth();

  if (!has({ plan: "pro" })) {
    return <p>Upgrade to Pro to access this content.</p>;
  }

  return <h1>Pro Content</h1>;
}
```

```tsx
import { auth } from "@clerk/nextjs/server";

export default async function AiGeneratePage() {
  const { has } = await auth();

  if (!has({ feature: "ai_flashcard_generation" })) {
    return <p>AI flashcard generation requires a Pro subscription.</p>;
  }

  return <h1>Generate Flashcards with AI</h1>;
}
```

### Client-side — `<Show>`

Use `<Show>` to conditionally render UI based on a plan or feature. Pass a `fallback` for users without access.

```tsx
import { Show } from "@clerk/nextjs";

<Show
  when={{ plan: "pro" }}
  fallback={<p>Upgrade to Pro to unlock this feature.</p>}
>
  <ProFeatureWidget />
</Show>

<Show
  when={{ feature: "unlimited_decks" }}
  fallback={<p>You have reached the free deck limit.</p>}
>
  <CreateDeckButton />
</Show>
```

## Rules

- Use `has({ plan: "..." })` or `has({ feature: "..." })` for server-side gating.
- Use `<Show when={{ plan: "..." }}>` or `<Show when={{ feature: "..." }}>` for client-side gating.
- Always reference plans and features by their exact slugs listed above.
- Do not create custom subscription logic or integrate Stripe directly — Clerk handles all payment processing.
- Place the pricing page at `/pricing` using the `<PricingTable />` component.
